            Tools: Sublime, Atom, Github, Adobe Photoshop, Postman, Heroku, MongoDB</p></div>
          <div class="col s3 offset-s1"><img src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/C5603AQFH2j__1g97qw/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/0?e=1526688000&v=alpha&t=5tQc96-0LJZ7hMFzizaHtUszaA9cjVqpxnw1WZqFZCY" class="profilem"><p>Web Development student in the San Francisco Bay Area learning new technologies and build on different skills. Would love to collaborate on new projects.
            Skills: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, jQuery, AJAX/JSON,Ruby, Node.js, Angular, Ruby on Rails, React, API integration, OOP, mySQL, Bootstrap, MongoDB, Express.js
            Github: https://github.com/Manjilan
            Website: http://manjilanakarmi.com</p></div>
          <div class="col s3 offset-s1"><img src="https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/C5603AQFljn9hFHfBQQ/profile-displayphoto-shrink_800_800/0?e=1526688000&v=alpha&t=kw1VNqZqwmYO7zGk0a_nayrwYa2Koqu0P5dVZf0XnZw" class="profileg"><p>The tech industry has transformative powers and as a developer, my aim is to utilize these to solve business challenges and build beautiful and meaningful things.
            Skills: Javascript, AJAX, JQuery, Node.js/Express, Ruby, Ruby on Rails, PostgreSQL, MsSQL, MongoDB, React, HTML5, CSS3 </p></div>
          </div>

      </main>
